Package com.platform.auth.internal

Class OAuth2Provider

java.lang.Object
com.platform.auth.internal.OAuth2Provider
@Entity public class OAuth2Provider extends Object
OAuth2 Provider entity representing configured OAuth2 authentication providers Stores provider configuration and metadata for Google, GitHub, Microsoft, etc.

This entity is part of the auth module's internal domain model and should not be directly exposed outside the auth module boundary.
